<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Citizen Knowledge</title>
<meta name="description" content="A daily record of ordinary news stories mapped against The Performance of Obedience.">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/style.css' | url }}">
</head>
<body>

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">A companion record to The Performance of Obedience</p>
    <h1 class="title">Citizen Knowledge</h1>
    <p class="strapline">Ordinary news, examined one story at a time against the same question: what do these events reveal about how modern institutions actually operate?

Over time, the record speaks for itself.
</p>
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span>{{ collections.posts.length }} ENTRIES</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<nav class="toc">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a href="{{ '/chapters/' | url }}">Browse by chapter</a>
    <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}">About this record</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>
  <div class="wrap">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="entry">
      <span class="stamp">
        <span class="label">Maps to The Performance of Obedience</span>
        Part {{ post.data.part }}: {{ post.data.partTitle }} &rarr; Chapter {{ post.data.chapter }}: {{ post.data.chapterTitle }}{% if post.data.subheading %} &rarr; {{ post.data.subheading }}{% endif %}
      </span>
      <h2>
        {% if post.data.deep_read %}<span class="deep-read-badge">Deep Read &mdash; With Manuscript</span>{% endif %}
        <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="source-line">{{ post.data.source }}</p>
      <p class="dek">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="signup-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Receive new ledger entries by email</p>
      <form
        action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/citizenknowledge"
        method="post"
        class="embeddable-buttondown-form"
      >
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="you@example.com" />
        <input type="hidden" value="1" name="embed" />
        <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" />
        <p class="signup-note">
          <a href="https://buttondown.com" target="_blank">Powered by Buttondown.</a>
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p><strong>ABOUT THIS RECORD</strong></p>
    <p>Citizen Knowledge is an ongoing public record accompanying *The Performance of Obedience* by Greg Lewis.

Each entry examines one ordinary news story through the same analytical framework, documenting recurring patterns in how institutions operate. Over time, those patterns form a record larger than any individual headline.

No images or verbatim text are reproduced from source publications. All summaries are original paraphrase, attributed by publication and date.

© Greg Lewis 2026
</p>
    <p><a href="{{ '/feed.xml' | url }}">RSS feed</a></p>
    <p>&copy; Greg Lewis 2026</p>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
